    "Co-occurrence analysis is where the relatedness of items is determined based on the number of documents in which they occur together.",
    "The unit of analysis is all keywords (author keywords and index keywords).",
    "We selected fractional counting instead of full counting.",
    "Fractional counting means that the weight of a link is fractionalised.",
    "The minimum of occurrences of a term was set to 10."
